---
title: Turkey and Zucchini Rigatoni with Parmesan Blush Sauce
description: This creamy, tomato-based blush sauce with ground turkey and tender zucchini makes a perfect light, tasty pasta. This dish comes together quickly and is brightened up with a touch of fresh herbs!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/turkey-and-zucchini-rigatoni-4bdc309e.jpg
